text: Samuel Theodore Liccardo (born April 16, 1970) is an American lawyer and politician whho became the U.S. representative from California's 16th congressional district. Before, he was the 65th mayor of San Jose from 2015 to 2023. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from San Jose, California Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
